Epuck Python Client for Newport's Communication Experiments
============================================================
Based on Epuck BTCOM (selector pose 3), Python2.6 multi-processing-
5 submodules are planned:
- DeviceController (Myro 2.8.16 E-puck Programming Interface)
- PoseUpdater (listen to DBus RobotPose signal from SwisTrack D-Bus Server Component)
- TaskInfoUpdater (listen to DBus TaskInfo signal from SwisTrack D-Bus Server Component)
- TaskSelector (Based on Attractive Field Model)
- DataLogger (To plot in LiveGraph)